家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=1d173551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf9e1933b7fcf290bc88efb4389ace83593ba09","tid":1742473,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"好明 但次次出到黎見到咁多手足<br />\n就知道原來 仲有好多屋企人同朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}